So proud of the very talented @chefgillesepie for this amazing article in The Washington Post! I mean,Come on- How cool is that???
You are the toast of the town once again Gilles! Bravo to all the staff of the new restaurant L’Avant Garde in Georgetown, what a tremendous accomplishment! #michelinstarchef #georgetown #thewashingtonpost #L’avantgarde ❤️❤️❤️

Sunday gardening, I love the smell and feel of freshly mowed grass…I’m in my happy place!
Wishing you all a wonderful start to a new week and a new month filled with adventure !!!
#HG, #lifestyle #happygirl #springtime @chefgillesepie Love you forever! 💕💕💕💕💕
Have a great week everyone, and Happy May 1st!🌸🌸🌸@chefgillesepie #goodlife #beingmybestself

BLT and oh so Yummy!❤️
So, everyone is always asking me OMG, you’re married to a French Michelin Star Chef? What in the world do you cook for him?
Well…after 27 years married to @chefgillesepie I’m a pretty good chef myself🤩 But guess what? Sometimes the best thing you can make for a French chef is a traditional American BLT!
#homemade #madewithlove #mychef #insanelydelicious 
This is what my husband craves on his day off! ❤️❤️❤️

For those of you who truly know me, you know that flowers are the way to my heart…These gorgeous flowers( from Trader Joe’s-I kid you not) are called peony tulips, aren’t they beautiful? And did you know that once they are cut they continue to grow, sometimes up to 6 inches! It’s because they have cells in their stems which respond to a plant hormone called auxin…isn’t that awesome? I wish it worked on humans!!!! 💕💕💕💕 
Have a blessed day everyone and remember to always be grateful! @chefgillesepie @sarafantastic #lifeisprecious #gratitude #loveyoualwaysandforever ❤️
Way back when….circa 1989 perhaps,( not exactly sure) photo by Davis Factor #theearlyyears #elitemodels #foreveryoung #sogratefulforalloftheamazingexperiencesibehad❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️
Friday Mood… Wonderful weekend with my husband in North Carolina. Have a beautiful day my friends!  @chefgillesepie #love #livingmybestlife #happygirl 💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💕

Felling oh-so-beachy with my Eynack sunglasses, I LOVE them!💕 This little adventure with @chefgillesepie visiting our darling friends @jpkruko73 and @benedouillecacahuete at their lovely home in OBX- Thank you guys for a lovely weekend! #livingmybestlife #happygirl #grateful #beachlife ❤️❤️❤️
Having a blast in North Carolina with this guy! @chefgillesepie  #weekendvibes #happy #livingmybestlife Have a fabulous and fun weekend everyone!!!!❤️

Happy Mothers Day to all my mommy friends! May we continue to cherish every moment with our children, continue to have the strength and patience to persevere through life’s ups and downs…knowing it truly is worth it all! @oliviersayshi - thank you for choosing me to be your mother, I am honored! 💕💕💕💕@chefgillesepie #mothersday #blessed #superheros #livingmybestlife #happymommy

Trying on ( what feels like hundreds) hues of blue for my son @oliviersayshi and his absolutely amazing and beautiful fiancé @cameryn.stone for their wedding on July 1st…. I’m of course over the moon, ( but I really want to have a beautiful dress) I had no idea how difficult this would be!
Anyway- of course it doesn’t matter what I wear- it’s all about them, but I want to make them proud of me! Is that silly?
Love these two love bugs more than anything -I believe in celebrating LOVE!!!!!💕💕💕 @chefgillesepie #weddingbliss #brideandgroom #loveatfirstsight #happymommy #loveyouforever #truelove 💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💕We are all so excited for them- I love you Cameryn and Olivier! Always and forever!!!!❤️

Hello my friends…hello my enemies( We can’t be sure just because someone is following us these days that they actually LIKE you!)
This lovely gentleman, a pelican (for those of you who are not knowledgeable in this species of bird), needs a name!  A grand and prestigious  name (s’il vous plaît)…after all, he does come from Palm Beach and was gifted to me by my very dear friend Barbara Becker( whom I absolutely adore). He truly holds his own in our small, but quaint garden in Old Town Alexandria. He has unusual eyes that give him an air of arrogance but he is quite a gentle bird…Any suggestions would be greatly appreciated - I think he is tired of being called Mr Pelican ( he deserves a much more honorable name).
Thank you from both myself and Mr Pelican! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️
Have a fabulous weekend !!!!
Thank you! #weekendvibes #gardengirl #lovinglife #happyandhealthy 💕💕💕

Love seeing my favorite guy so happy @chefgillesepie . Thanks to @fredjoulin for putting together this amazing event in Miami for the Maîtres Cuisiniers de France, it’s an honor to be surrounded by such great talents! Special merci to @jpkruko73 -always a ray of sunshine 💕
And of course, thank you to Grand Beach Hotel Surfside for the exceptional accommodations for all of us( we will be back!💕) #merci #miamibeach #foodieforever #inlovewithmychef Oh- and I almost forgot- Thank you @katystrouk and @roxannestrouk for Gilles birthday t-shirt ( so appropriate 🤩)
